Short:

This is R-Kive! A three-CD, 37 tracks, near-four-hour,
chronologically-assembled collection of songs taken from
the albums of Genesis, and from the albums of Rutherford,
Tony Banks, Peter Gabriel, Phil Collins and Steve Hackett.

